hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections

Class ObjectStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.ObjectStack

  • public class ObjectStack
extends Object
    This class is representation of stack for storing objects. It uses implementation of ArrayBackedIndexedCollection through a Adaptor pattern where this class is Adaptor.
    Author:
    Vilim Staroveški
